          "text": "**DO-330 TQL ↔ ISO 26262 TCL Conceptual Mapping** (not formally standardized):\n\nImportant: No official cross-standard mapping exists. DO-330 defines 5 TQL levels (TQL-1 most rigorous), ISO 26262 Part 8 defines 3 TCL levels (TCL3 highest confidence). Both frameworks assess tool risk through impact and error detection capability, but differ structurally. DO-330 is noted as applicable cross-domain, but the mapping below represents conceptual parallels, not normative correspondence."
